Usage: resizeBlackBox [-help] <blackBoxName> { -aspectRatio <float> | { [-width <float>] [ -height <float> ]}}

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxName>           # Specifies the name of the blackbox.
                         # (string, required)
-aspectRatio <float>     # Specifies the new aspect ratio, which is height
                         # divided by width, with the blackbox area constant.
                         # (float, optional)
-height <float>          # Specifies the new height in user units.
                         # (float, optional)
-width <float>           # Specifies the new width in user units.
                         # (float, optional)